# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HydroTrack Frontend — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in YOUR OWN values.
# Never commit .env.local — it is already in .gitignore.
#
# HOW TO GET THESE VALUES:
#   1. Create a free Supabase project at https://supabase.com
#      → Project Settings → API → copy URL and anon key
#   2. Deploy the /backend to a HuggingFace Space (see SETUP.md)
#      → your Space URL will be https://YOUR-USERNAME-hydrotrack-api.hf.space
#   3. Run: python scripts/generate-vapid.py
#      → copy the printed public key here
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://YOUR-HF-USERNAME-hydrotrack-api.hf.space
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-ID.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key-here
VITE_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=your-vapid-public-key-here
